Cap
===


What is Cap ?
-------------

 Cap is simple snippet manager for programmers. Cap is quick and clean on your file system.


Install
-------

	$ git clone https://github.com/narupo/cap
	$ cd cap/src
	$ make && sudo make install


Example
-------

	$ cap
	$ cap home
	$ cap ls

	$ cap home /my/snippet/file/directory
	$ cap ls

